node.title: Two arrested after New Year's Eve motorbike road through Auckland
node.description: Two men have been arrested and five dirt bikes have been impounded.
node.content: ["Two men have been arrested and five dirt bikes have been impounded following a reckless New Year's Eve ride through Auckland.", "Inspector Jacqui Whittaker said many cyclists and drivers had to take evasive action to protect themselves from the group, none of whom had a valid licence to ride the bikes.", "Whittaker said many of the riders were also extremely aggressive towards police and a patrol car was damaged.", "The two arrested men face charges including failing to stop, careless driving and driving without a licence.", "RNZ", "\u00a0"]
